1370: Thieleman moved to Die Camp.B.13 after marriage.
Got married to Ghoudekinen at age 20 in 1370.
1372: Had a daughter with Ghoudekinen, Gheesen, at age 22.
1373: Had a son with Ghoudekinen, Hughe, at age 23.
1374: Had a son with Ghoudekinen, Daniel, at age 24.
1375: Had a daughter with Ghoudekinen, Sara, at age 25.
1376: Lost daughter Gheesen when Gheesen was 5 years old.
1377: Had a son with Ghoudekinen, Brun, at age 27.
1378: Lost his wife Ghoudekinen while she was giving birth to Baua in 1378.
Became caretaker of Hughe, Daniel, Sara, Brun, Baua at age 29.
1390: Lost son Hughe when Hughe was 18 years old.
